object = defaultSetup
assert set(sections).issubset(object.dataDict.keys())
assert set(inlistpgstarParameters).issubset(object.dataDict['pgstar'][
    'inlist_pgstar'].keys())
assert set(inlistProjectParametersStarJob).issubset(object.dataDict[
    'star_job']['inlist_project'].keys())
assert set(inlistProjectParametersControl).issubset(object.dataDict[
    'controls']['inlist_project'].keys())
object['initial_mass'] = 5
assert object['controls']['inlist_project']['initial_mass'] == 5
object['initial_mass'] = 10
assert object['controls']['inlist_project']['initial_mass'] == 10
object.addValue('saved_model_for_merger_1', 'text')
assert object['star_job']['inlist_project']['saved_model_for_merger_1'
    ] == 'text'
object.removeValue('saved_model_for_merger_1')
with pytest.raises(KeyError):
    object.addValue('dummy', 'dummy')
